Constructor Detail

ReviewIdSelectionWizard

public ReviewIdSelectionWizard(java.lang.String reviewPhaseNameKey,
                               org.eclipse.core.resources.IProject defaultProject,
                               boolean isMultipleChoiceEnabled)
Instantiates review id selection wizard. After this wizard is finished, 1) review ID (determined by defaultProject name and review id) will be set to content provider model, 2) reviewer ID was set to preference store.

Parameters:
reviewPhaseNameKey - the review phase name key.
defaultProject - the defaultProject to be shown as a default in the dialog. Clients can not pass defaultProject as null. so that they should check the null before instantiating this.
isMultipleChoiceEnabled - set true if the defaultProject choice is multiple. false if the defaultProject choice is only the passing defaultProject.
